[340.117149, "o", "4 nested rotated bowls:\r\n  Range: x=0..9, y=0..11\r\n  Size: 10x12\r\nBall at y offset 12: x=0..9, y=12..19\r\nCombined: 10x20x6 = 1200\r\nBall at by=12 with 4 bowls: 10x20x6 = 1200\r\n"]
